---
description: Backend architecture rules
globs:
  - backend/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Backend owns:
- auth
- sessions
- Drive Discovery
- POI selection
- ETA logic
- trigger logic
- narration orchestration
- privacy/history controls

Rules:
- TypeScript + Express
- thin controllers
- business logic in services
- explicit DTOs and interfaces
- config-driven thresholds only
- no Google keys in mobile-facing logic
- no LLM decision-making for POI selection or trigger timing
- add state-machine logic explicitly, do not hide it in ad hoc conditions